<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Surat Sponsor Visa</title></head>
<body style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5;">
<p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;font-size:13pt;border:1px dashed #999;padding:10px;">[ KOP SURAT PERUSAHAAN / TOKO ]<br/><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:10pt;">(Nama perusahaan, alamat lengkap, no. telepon — atau gunakan kop resmi)</span></p>
<br/>
<p style="text-align:right;">Jakarta, ______________ 20___</p>
<br/>
<p>To:<br/>
<b>Visa Section of</b><br/>
<b>EMBASSY OF [NEGARA TUJUAN]</b><br/>
Jakarta</p>
<br/>
<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
<p>With this letter, I would like to inform you that I am the undersigned,</p>
<table cellpadding="3" style="font-size:12pt;">
<tr><td style="width:160px;">Name</td><td>: [NAMA YANG MENSPONSORI]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Position</td><td>: [POSISI / JABATAN YANG MENSPONSORI]</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Certify that,</p>
<table cellpadding="3" style="font-size:12pt;">
<tr><td style="width:160px;">Name</td><td>: [NAMA PEMOHON — SESUAI PASPOR]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Position</td><td>: [POSISI PEMOHON DI PERUSAHAAN]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Passport No</td><td>: [NO. PASPOR PEMOHON]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Working Since</td><td>: [MASA KERJA / SEJAK KAPAN]</td></tr>
</table>
<p style="font-size:10pt;color:#666;">(Bila ada anggota keluarga yang ikut, tambahkan:)</p>
<table cellpadding="3" style="font-size:12pt;">
<tr><td style="width:160px;">Name</td><td>: [NAMA KELUARGA YANG IKUT — SESUAI PASPOR]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Relation</td><td>: [HUBUNGAN DENGAN PEMOHON]</td></tr>
<tr><td>Passport No</td><td>: [NO. PASPOR KELUARGA]</td></tr>
</table>
<br/>
<p>are planning to have a vacation to <b>[NEGARA TUJUAN]</b>, including your country, on <b>[TANGGAL BERANGKAT]</b> until <b>[TANGGAL PULANG]</b> (and will return to Indonesia afterwards).</p>
<p>I acknowledge and guarantee that he/she/they will not seek any employment or permanent stay in your country and will return to Indonesia soon after the holiday trip is completed. All kinds of expenses during the trip for the above purpose are fully covered by [the company / my personal account].</p>
<p>Kindly grant them the necessary entry visa in order to join the tour program. Your kind assistance will be highly appreciated.</p>
<br/>
<p>Sincerely yours,<br/><span style="font-size:10pt;color:#666;">(distempel &amp; ditandatangani oleh yang mensponsori)</span></p>
<br/><br/>
<p style="font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;">[NAMA YANG MENSPONSORI]</p>
<p>[POSISI / JABATAN]</p>
<br/>
<p style="font-size:9pt;color:#777;border-top:1px solid #ccc;padding-top:6pt;">Petunjuk: ganti semua bagian dalam tanda kurung siku [ ]. Cetak di atas kop surat perusahaan/toko, bubuhi stempel &amp; tanda tangan, lalu scan/foto untuk diunggah. Bila sponsor pribadi (bukan perusahaan), kop surat bisa dihilangkan &amp; gunakan data pribadi sponsor.</p>
</body></html>
